  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study evaluates the impact of essential oils massage on anxiety of patients who are
      suffering from cancer at a metastasis stage. Half of patients will be massaged first by
      essential oils and then by oil only. The other half will be massaged first by oil and then by
      essential oils.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
